fibonacci(int) - Static method in class IntegerComputer
Computes the Fibonacci number with index equal to the specified integer:
f(0) = 1, f(1) = 1, f(n) = f(n-2) + f(n-1) for n greater than 1.

Computes the triangular number with the specified index:
